message.body: Good morning! Are you free Thurs evening for drinks?
Hey! Yeah! I am going to be climbing the chapel from 5:30-6:30 but anytime after will work
Great! I get home while you're climbing anyway, so after is good. Wanna say 7pm? And let's stay in ######...maybe ######## on Main?
Yeah that works. I've never been to ####. A restaurant?
Just a bar, but you can order food from############# and they bring it in.
Oo okie yeah that sounds perfect at 7!
